--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
C: change
E: enhancement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 4.2.0 (2019-05-26)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.8

* Version 4.1.0 (2019-04-27)
F: Add support for OpenBSD 6.5
F: Drop support for OpenBSD 6.4

* Version 4.0.0 (2019-01-24)
C: Rename option 'ntpd_monitor_mail_recipient' to 'ntpd_monitor_mail_from_address'
C: Rename option 'ntpd_monitor_mail_sender' to 'ntpd_monitor_mail_to_address'

* Version 3.2.2 (2019-01-22)
E: Improve script by throwing error message if script is executed interactively

* Version 3.2.1 (2019-01-21)
E: Improve script and reduce noise by removing echo command from alerting function

* Version 3.2.0 (2019-01-13)
C: Add support for FreeBSD 12.0-RELEASE
C: Drop support for FreeBSD 11.2-RELEASE

* Version 3.1.4 (2019-01-09)
B: Fix issue introduced with improvements to prevent globbing and word splitting

* Version 3.1.3 (2019-01-09)
B: Improve return value verification and fix unexpected operator/operand issue
E: Improve Shell script to prevent globbing and word splitting

* Version 3.1.2 (2018-12-27)
E: Minor style improvement

* Version 3.1.1 (2018-12-10)
B: Fix 'mailx' command for OpenBSD systems

* Version 3.1.0 (2018-12-10)
F: Add option to set system time offset limit (ntpd_check_time_offset_limit)
E: Improve system time offset check
E: Remove needless remove tasks

* Version 3.0.1 (2018-12-09)
E: Minor Jinja2 parameter improvement

* Version 3.0.0 (2018-12-08)
F: Redesign 'ntpd_server' parameter
F: Redesign 'ntpd_restrict' parameter
F: Add 'ntpd_check-time' health check

* Version 2.5.2 (2018-12-07)
E: Remove 'ntpd_monitor_mail_subject' parameter

* Version 2.5.1 (2018-12-07)
E: Remove email information from message

* Version 2.5.0 (2018-10-20)
F: Add support for OpenBSD 6.4
F: Drop support for OpenBSD 6.3

* Version 2.4.3 (2018-07-21)
